  <description>
    <p>
	ArcTexel is a universal 2D editor designed for all kinds of creative work. Whether you want to make game sprites, paint illustrations, design logos, edit images, or create animations, ArcTexel gives you the tools to bring your ideas to life—all in a clean and familiar interface.
    </p>
    <p>
	Powered by a Node Graph for advanced, non-destructive editing, ArcTexel comes with three unique toolsets that can be used together on the same canvas:
    </p>
    <p>
	Pixel Art – pixel-perfect drawing tools for sprites and retro graphics
	Painting – soft brushes, smooth lines, and anti-aliased shapes
		    Vector – scalable paths and shapes for logos and clean designs
    </p>
  </description>
  
